n係有意圖咁樣做 佢寧願唔教波都唔會咁做<br />\n<br />\n比爾沙話佢承認兼且自己負全責<br />\n但係佢建基於<br />\n1. 無違反明文規則（亦無侵入私家範圍）<br />\n2. 道德上可能有唔啱 佢承認<br />\n3. 其實佢靠data analysis已經攞到好足夠嘅資料 但係都有機會會輸波 （之後叫啲記者揀場波等佢即場解釋）<br />\n4. 所以佢接受唔到放過任何一絲可以贏得場比賽嘅機會 包括規則無寫明唔比嘅「睇人哋訓練」<br />\n5.佢對隊隊都有咁做 唔止打比郡 而以前喺西班牙阿根廷都係咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n咁過咗個lecture 大眾反應係欣賞比爾沙呢種workaholic <br />\n兼且大方承認自己做過 你罰咪罰我負全責嘅態度<br />\n之後林柏特嘅回覆係「隊隊都有data analysis架啦 有咩特別」「其他地方咁做 唔代表我buy呢種方法」「哥狗肥普讚比爾沙係私人讚又唔係公開讚」咪變咗好似怨婦咁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theweek.co.uk/football/99037/leeds-derby-spygate-marcelo-bielsa-powerpoint-presentation-best-tweets-reactions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F99037%2Fleeds-derby-spygate-marcelo-bielsa-powerpoint-presentation-best-tweets-reactions&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=6b4e0455\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theweek.co.uk/football/99037/leeds-derby-spygate-marcelo-bielsa-powerpoint-presentation-best-tweets-reactions</a>"},{"pid":"7d4976d8bfa643b5f0ca417f54560b2b1f3efa21","tid":2114162,"uid":39812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T22:19:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ClsORIWnbQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FClsORIWnbQY&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=2d60c6f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ClsORIWnbQY</a>"},{"pid":"d48accbda7b6fb943dff90f5b36ed39017394bbc","tid":2114162,"uid":74957,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"072ebf2d25d1c49e7102e152c066235309ceab1b","tid":2114162,"uid":39812,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"73c60fa9784293c83ff050db7d15be77d5537aec","tid":2114162,"uid":2169,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2adbac01ab972476982db8edce38c1726b17c9d6","tid":2114162,"uid":39812,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"做阿根廷帶隊教過肥普施蒙尼<br />\n教智利幫智利打好個底 奠定10年代嘅主力 但係佢唔撚妥個新足協主席所以劈炮<br />\n母會阿根廷紐維爾舊生個球場用佢來命名<br 